What did you do, kiddo?

09:25.720 --> 09:28.880
You are not taking
my fucking boat, OK?

09:29.080 --> 09:31.280
You don't want
to be drawing attention to yourselves.

09:31.360 --> 09:32.360
Take my word for it.

09:35.400 --> 09:39.040
OK. Everybody, just sit down,
and calm down.

09:40.080 --> 09:41.960
You're safe here, OK?

09:43.400 --> 09:44.400
