about your little boy?

11:27.560 --> 11:28.560
Because...

11:31.760 --> 11:35.280
Ah, shit.
Because I was embarrassed, OK?

11:36.480 --> 11:37.720
Because I felt ashamed.

11:40.040 --> 11:41.160
He's called Milton.

11:42.440 --> 11:43.360
He's eight.

11:45.240 --> 11:47.600
He's weirdly good at spelling.

11:48.680 --> 11:50.400
I'm sorry, I should have said.

11:52.120 --> 11:54.200
Can we start again

