-There was a man.
-Alyssa...

12:03.080 --> 12:04.040
OK...

12:06.120 --> 12:07.120
We killed him.

12:09.200 --> 12:10.040
OK.

12:11.120 --> 12:12.720
Don't worry, it's OK.

12:16.040 --> 12:17.880
He was going to hurt me.

12:19.200 --> 12:20.400
Oh, darling.

12:21.160 --> 12:22.400
He was bad.

12:25.240 --> 12:26.760
He was really bad.

12:28.800 --> 12:30.240
