16:19.720 --> 16:21.000
I feel like I'm going mad.

16:21.080 --> 16:22.800
Hey! To be mad in a deranged--

16:22.880 --> 16:25.680
Shut up! Shut the fuck up!
Stop quoting yourself!

16:34.120 --> 16:37.480
Will we go to prison if we hand
ourselves in Will we?

